dcterms:description: A dataset whose samples are graphs representing proteins. In each graph, the nodes represent the secondary structure elements and have labels of helix, sheet, or turn. If two nodes are neighbors along the amino acid sequence or in 3D space, there is an undirected edge connecting them.
dcterms:title: PROTEINS

dcterms:creator: N. Wale
G. Karypis
dcterms:description: A balanced dataset of chemical compounds screened for activity against non-small cell lung cancer. Each graph in NCI1 represents a chemical compound, where the nodes, node labels, edges are related to the atoms, atom types, and chemical bonds, respectively.
dcterms:title: NCI1

dcterms:creator: Pinar Yanardag
S.V.N. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: A scientific collaboration dataset derived from three scientific collaboration datasets, namely, High Energy Physics, Condensed Matter Physics, and Astro Physics. The graphs are the ego-networks of different researchers from each field.
dcterms:title: COLLAB

dcterms:creator: Pinar Yanardag
S.V.N. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: Datasets of movie collaborations containing ego-networks derived from each actor/actress by the collaboration relations. The labels of the graphs in IMDB-BINARY are genres of Action and Romance.
dcterms:title: IMDB-BINARY

dcterms:creator: Pinar Yanardag
S.V.N. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: Datasets of movie collaborations containing ego-networks derived from each actor/actress by the collaboration relations. The IMDB-MULTI dataset has graph labels according to genres of Comedy, Romance, and Sci-Fi.
dcterms:title: IMDB-MULTI

dcterms:creator: Pinar Yanardag
S.V.N. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: Balanced datasets similar to the IMDB-BINARY dataset. Each graph in REDDIT datasets represents an online discussion thread by representing the users as nodes in the graph.
dcterms:title: REDDIT-BINARY

dcterms:creator: Pinar Yanardag
S.V.N. Vishwanathan
dcterms:description: Balanced datasets similar to the IMDB-MULTI dataset. Each graph in REDDIT-MULTI-5K has labels according to their subreddits.
dcterms:title: REDDIT-MULTI-5K
